{"tid":2413130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[估國家] 獸父逼10歲女兒穿情趣內衣　性侵590次！她隱忍6年最後希望仍落空","createTime":"2021-02-18T12:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T15:12:55.000Z","uid":17387,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fbde925c937751386bdc86f38540e68362ad42ef","tid":2413130,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/qklCRxo5xnDIIaGeGpto7mDGfUY=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGFYI4IHXUKSAVZ2P6DWW5XBPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqklCRxo5xnDIIaGeGpto7mDGfUY%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGFYI4IHXUKSAVZ2P6DWW5XBPQ.jpg&h=268160fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台南市一名狼父從2012年9月起趁妻子上大夜班，對當時只有10歲女兒伸狼爪，逼女兒穿情趣內衣，對她使用情趣用品，最後性侵女兒，他以事情曝光會導致「爸媽離婚」，逼女兒不准聲張，女兒為此隱忍6年，直到狼父因詐欺罪遭警方羈押，少女才告訴學校輔導老師，但其父母最後仍在2017年離婚，讓她希望落空。檢警發現，狼父以每周兩次性侵女兒，6年共590次，台南地院依強制性交罪判處12年。<br />\n<br />\n台南地院法官認為，被告沒有克制性衝動，為滿足一己色慾，罔顧人倫，多次性侵女兒，不尊重女兒的身體自主權，造成身心受創並留下難以磨滅陰影，嚴重影響其人格發展的健全，毀損被害人對兩性關係及家庭觀念認知，難以彌補的傷害。法官認為被告對未滿14歲女子犯強制性交罪共590次，各處7年8月徒刑，應執行12年徒刑，全案可上訴二審。<br />\n<br />\n一審判決書指出，被告從2012年9月開始竟趁著妻子（已於2017年初離婚）晚間到電子遊樂場上班時，性侵就讀國小3年級、年僅10歲女兒，他以每周2次頻率在租屋處房間、客廳等處，違反女兒意願，強脫對方衣服，要求女兒穿情趣內衣後，幫他口交，他還以跳蛋、按摩棒等多種情趣用品侵入女兒下體，最後性侵女兒。被告還威脅女兒不能告訴他人，否則事情曝光，他會跟母親離婚，女兒就沒有媽媽了。<br />\n<br />\n少女擔心父母離婚，且覺得反抗無用，心灰意冷，沒有積極反抗，從2012年9月到2018年4月，默默隱忍6年，以每周2次計算，共遭侵犯590次，上學時還會崩潰流淚。2018年5月間，少女見到父親因詐欺案件遭警方逮捕、法院羈押，她覺得「終於安全」，才由同學陪同、告訴輔導老師，揭露父親獸行。<br />\n<br />\n警方在被告租屋處房間找到2件情趣內衣、跳蛋、電動按摩棒及潤滑液。被告否認犯行，辯稱少女交友網絡複雜，曾在網路詐欺他人，有說謊的人格特質，說法不可採信；但法官院勘驗各項事證後，不採信被告說詞，認為少女沒有誣陷親生父親的理由。（地方中心辛啟松／台南報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210218/7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0QMPlWQ7K1aNlcRSsHuws08FnG2SVBMKla4v6gUk7H7YNcC5DTUgntAjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0QMPlWQ7K1aNlcRSsHuws08FnG2SVBMKla4v6gUk7H7YNcC5DTUgntAjA&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69HlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=0321e04f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0QMPlWQ7K1aNlcRSsHuws08FnG2SVBMKla4v6gUk7H7YNcC5DTUgntAjA&h=60cdd8d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210218/7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0QMPlWQ7K1aNlcRSsHuws08FnG2SVBMKla4v6gUk7H7YNcC5DTUgntAjA</a><br />\n<br />\n台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505cb44737690d9e8d073aa00be51430374cbdde","tid":2413130,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"台南咁都有一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d4d90e21668da58ccb1f95a12541d9567aa58a","tid":2413130,"uid":252605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"505cb44737690d9e8d073aa00be51430374cbdde","tid":2413130,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"台南咁都有一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"新北最近冇乜分"},{"pid":"3ce186562126b7beff2ab105fabf0610b7569f6f","tid":2413130,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d4d90e21668d